				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ch%E1%BB%89-T%C3%ADn/Cung-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0u-C%E1%BA%A7u-An-Nam-ch%C6%B0-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%A7n-thi/poem-_GmYFQkVy6PF7Jo_VnmtjA">Cung hoạ ngự chế tứ Triều Tiên, Lưu Cầu, An Nam chư quốc sứ thần thi - 恭和御制賜朝鮮琉球安南諸國使臣詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ch%E1%BB%89-T%C3%ADn/author-TkXgyRqhWylbpzLASwFR3g">Nguyễn Chỉ Tín</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Cao-T%E1%BB%95-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-rlUTzed0jUcS2OJkq_MN_Q">Đề Cao Tổ miếu - 題高祖廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-K%C3%ADnh-%C3%81i-t%E1%BB%B1-l%C3%A2u/poem--7B1wnK3oOjHdCmWO56GqQ">Đề Kính Ái tự lâu - 題敬愛寺樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-giang-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-th%E1%BA%A3o-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-0125BTy6UD9DFdwphA4XNA">Ký đề giang ngoại thảo đường - 寄題江外草堂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%99-thu-u%E1%BB%95ng-B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ch%C3%A2u-th%E1%BB%A7-tr%C3%A1t-su%E1%BA%A5t-nh%C4%A9-khi%E1%BB%83n-h%E1%BB%A9ng-k%C3%BD-c%E1%BA%ADn-tr%C3%ACnh-T%C3%B4-Ho%C3%A1n-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-OBlyRxjh5TCqFh5dGFYn3g">Mộ thu uổng Bùi Đạo Châu thủ trát, suất nhĩ khiển hứng, ký cận trình Tô Hoán thị ngự - 暮秋枉裴道州手札，率爾遣興，寄近呈蘇渙侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>•